FPS-24. Her right hand, already raised near her face, moves slowly upward to softly trace the edge of her jawline. Fingers glide under her chin, drawing attention to her neckline as her head subtly tilts. Her expression softens, and her gaze gently drops downward. A deep breath lifts her chest as the satin fabric catches the shifting light. Her lips remain parted, skin glowing. A faint breeze causes a few strands of hair to move against her shoulder. The motion concludes with her hand resting just beneath her chin, body still and relaxed.

FPS-24. Her right hand lowers smoothly from her chin, gliding slowly down across her chest and over the satin fabric at her waist. The fingers trail lightly, brushing the curve of her body until they come to rest on her upper thigh. Her gaze remains downward, breath calm and visible in the slight lift of her shoulders. The silky fabric subtly shifts beneath her fingertips. Her expression stays serene, lips gently parted. A loose strand of hair drapes over her collarbone as she settles into complete stillness at the end.
